Title: Prayer Like Stones
---
A monk rose from his knees and
declared the grandeur of Godï¼š

All praise and glory are Yours,
Father, Son, and Holy Spirit.

Be quiet, hushed his brother
in the dark, from the next cell,

you dishonor the One
you most intend to praise.

Listen to this stone; it too
is an utterance of God.
